document_data.caption: A map of Moray showing the Last Head in the south.
document_data.name: Last Head
document_data.mainbody: The '''Last Head''' was a cape found on the island of [[Moray]] within the [[Moonshae Isles]].{{Cite dungeon/196/Backdrop: The Moonshae Isles}}
document_data.Geography: The cape was located at the southern tip of Moray, jutting south from the [[Orcskull Mountains]] for {{SI|10|mi|k|long=yes}} into the [[Trackless Sea]] where the [[Strait of the Leviathan]] began. The [[Ossian Reefs]] curved around the Last Head.
